@startuml
left to right direction

actor "Jogador" as Player

rectangle "Jogo 06 (Punch-Out)" {
  (Iniciar jogo) as UC_Start
  (Ver instrucoes) as UC_Instr
  (Sair) as UC_Exit
  (Atacar) as UC_Attack
  (Bloquear) as UC_Block
  (Pausar/Retomar) as UC_Pause
  (Reiniciar partida) as UC_Restart
  (Ver resultado) as UC_Result
  (Voltar ao menu) as UC_Menu
}

Player --> UC_Start
Player --> UC_Instr
Player --> UC_Exit
Player --> UC_Attack
Player --> UC_Block
Player --> UC_Pause
Player --> UC_Restart
Player --> UC_Result
Player --> UC_Menu

UC_Result .> UC_Restart : estende
UC_Result .> UC_Menu : estende
@enduml
